snippet.title: Super Mario Bros 2011: Attack of the Bloopers (Old Fangame Trailer)
snippet.description:
Celebrating over 30 Subscribers!

Wow. Over 5,000 views! Thank you all. The game should be done by the end of 2011(perfect since it is still in 2011).

Stupid Youtube ruined the quality, but the video does not matter. This is the first Preview of Super Mario Bros 2011. 
If you have enjoyed any of these fangames or games:
Super Mario Galaxy (Nintendo)
Super Mario Galaxy 2 (Nintendo)
Super Mario Bros 2010 (BuzzNBen)
---- You will enjoy this installment. This game is similar to one of the newest Mario Games "Super Mario Galaxy 2."

Updates:
12/10/10: Demo 2.0 is out on the Official Website. Go there and download it.
03/20/11: MFGG.net has Super Mario Bros 2011. You can download it there.
05/28/11: MFGG.net HAD Super Mario Bros 2011. YOU NOW CAN'T DOWNLOAD IT THERE!!
12/3/11: Were gonna finish this thing by the end of the month, hopely. :)
1/23/12: The full game will be released.
6/14/13: The full game with fixed bugs and problems is released.

Now for the links:

Directory to my MAIN webpage:
http://www.buzznben.com

Grand Final Release (Direct Download):
https://www.mediafire.com/file/97l72fbdpl2jhj0/Super_Mario_Bros_AOTB_Final.zip/file

All Sorts of Crazy Games including the downloads of Super Mario Bros 2010 and Super Mario Bros Doomsday:
http://www.buzznben.com/games.html

The Official Super Mario Bros 2011 Fansite with the release of Super Mario Bros 2011:
http://smb2011attackofthebloopers.weebly.com

Other:
http://www.youtube.com/BuzzNBen21
